systemServer

Class MessageUtils

  • java.lang.Object
    • systemServer.MessageUtils

  • public class MessageUtils
extends java.lang.Object
    This is an experiment with packing/unpacking messages Right now, this literally sends stuff in an array one string at a time. It is not efficient, but it's very easy to make new message types. If we make sure to pack/unpack messages here, we can easy switch out the logic and make it more efficient later!
